								attack on <term>mutʻah</term> marriage made in <persName role="aut" key="viaf_53999017">Shāh ʻAbd al-ʻAzīz Dihlavī</persName>'s
									<title key="work_9203">Tuḥfah-'i
								Is̱nā-ʻasharīyah</title>
                     </summary>
                     <msItem class="https://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh2012000504">
